Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}分裂的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}被撕裂的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}春雪終於站了起來
